title: Experience the Tramor Lifestyle😊
posting_body: ['There’s no place like home and there’s surely no place like Tramor at Oak Run!', 'Taking scenic living up a notch, our apartments offer you everything you need to lead the life you’ve always desired.', 'From beautiful views and professional staff, we’ve made sure to surpass expectations.', 'Our pet-friendly premise has no breed or weight restrictions and has a leash-free pet park where your furry friends can roam freely.', 'Explore all the possibilities that open for you as one of our residents!', 'Schedule your personal Virtual / In-Person Tour today!', '<URL>/', 'Unit Details:', '- Maple Floorplan', '- Faux Wood Flooring Throughout', '- Patio with Outdoor Storage Closet', '- Backyard', '- Dishwasher', '- Garbage Disposal', '- Air Conditioning/Central Heating/Ceiling Fan', '- Pets Welcomed (No Breed/Weight Restrictions!)', 'Property Details:', '- 32 Acres of Trees and Property Greenbelt Throughout', '- Three Swimming Pools with Sunbathing Decks', '-24 Hour Fitness Center', '- Tennis Courts', '- Gated Off-Leash Dog Park', 'On-Site', '- Three On-Site Laundry Facilities', '- 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', '- Within Walking Distance to Multiple Bus Lines', '- Close to Downtown, South 1st, and South Congress…Amazing Shopping and Dining!', 'Come visit us today!', 'Our office is open weekdays 9am to 6:00pm and Saturdays 10am to 2pm.', 'For all your leasing needs, ask for Brittany!', '😊']
